CAT3DAnnotationFilterHdr.Title: Annotation Sets Filter
CAT3DAnnotationFilterHdr.ShortHelp: Displays or hides the Annotation Sets filter panel.
CAT3DAnnotationFilterHdr.LongHelp: You can filter the annotation sets, annotations displayed in the 3D area, and the technological attributes.
CAT3DAnnotationOpenFavoriteCtxHdr.Title: Open in Favorite Context
CAT3DAnnotationOpenFavoriteCtxHdr.ShortH: Open the selected 3DShape in Favorite Context.
